https://github.com/sharkdp/fd?tab=readme-ov-file#installation

julials
https://discourse.julialang.org/t/neovim-lsp-in-julia-1-12/134003

nvim-treesitter
make sure `tree-sitter-cli` is installed
the easiest way is to do `npm install -g tree-sitter-cli`
run `:checkhealth nvim-treesitter` to see status of parsers and requirements
    note, this is different to `:checkhealth treesitter` for some reason
